schools.name: Pioneer Magnet School for the Visual and Performing Arts

data.description: EXTRA! EXTRA! read all about it! You could be the new owner of this lovely home in beautiful Pioneer, off Meadow Drive in Mace Meadows, perfect with beautiful surroundings and a serene escape. Seller calls it "Deerhaven." This split level home features 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom and a large kitchen with a corner window over double sinks. A large fireplace with beautiful rock design and cathedral ceiling describes the large family room. The downstairs features a large bonus room with a full bathroom, kitchenette, laundry room, a free-standing wood-burning stove and new carpeting. Each level has it's own large deck with open views of pine and oak trees. This home is perfect for quiet time, entertaining and is close to winter activities at Laken Tahoe and Kirkwood. Camping, fishing and hiking are the best anywhere. Large cabinets in the finished 2+ car garage provides lots of storage; room for everything. Home has newer A/C, newer roof, new water heater and freshly painted full decks. Don't miss this opportunity. No need to move from California. Come to Pioneer where the air is fresh and clean, the scenery is beautiful and the people are friendly.  Come see for yourself. You'll be glad you did! Incidentally, seller is only the second owner of this wonderful home. Make an offer.
